				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">To simulate the scanline gaps without losing brightness, we have to simulate the beam spreading. Here's the title screen of SMB1 with a very simplistic model of beam spreading. Click the attached image below.</div>

					
